    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system that remains sharp and responsive. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox offers tactile shift throws, sending power to a 3.21 ratio limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a reinforced rear subframe and a top-end refresh to ensure valvetrain longevity. The chassis dynamics are preserved through refreshed bushings and factory-spec dampers, providing the signature communicative steering feel. While the finish reflects its history as a driver's car, the mechanical synchronization and drivetrain rigidity are excellent.",
