      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity to own a well-cared-for model that balances reliability with a premium feel. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, though a discerning eye will notice a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch\u2014typical signs of careful road use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean; the seats are firm and free of any rips or stains, and the original carpets have been protected by floor mats since day one. All interior electronics, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system, function exactly as they should. Mechanically, the car is in robust health. It has been serviced at regular intervals, with the most recent oil change and multi-point inspection completed just last month. The engine runs quietly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the brakes provide confident stopping power. The tires show approximately 70% tread depth remaining, ensuring many more miles of worry-free driving. This car drives straight and true, offering a smooth, rattle-free experience that speaks to its consistent upkeep.",
